column5: I went out for a few hours tonight and hooked into my new PB muskie!   pulled this little bugger off of his head  Release shot  you can see the mark from the lampry
nice muskie nasty lamprey, looks like something I saw on the Xfiles
Great musky, glad you got rid of his third eye, that must have been bugging it for awhile.  Joey
Congrats on the new PB Jiggy. I'm sure it will be much happier without the hitch hiker.
Congrates on the new PB    I'm sure he's glad to have had his cling-on removed...that's one nasty mark it left.
Beautiful Ski getnjiggywithit Congratulations on your PB  Great job and thanks for sharing Leechman
I don't know what felt better having the hook out of it's mouth or the teeth out of it's head.  Outstanding job, what a catch man!  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
nice fish....  the next person that catches is gonna wonder where it third eye went though
